padgroup Control permute
twpin_clk nonfixed
twpin_rst_n nonfixed
restrict side T

padgroup Command permute
twpin_cmd_valid nonfixed
twpin_cmd_ready nonfixed
twpin_cmd_last nonfixed
restrict side L

padgroup Response permute
twpin_rsp_valid nonfixed
twpin_rsp_ready nonfixed
twpin_rsp_last nonfixed
twpin_busy nonfixed
restrict side R
